      "file_path": "models-examples/src/main/resources/policytypes/onap.policies.native.Drools.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 5,
      "line": 40,
      "message": "I think we have to do check on the pdp-d side regardless, every time we get one of these policies.   It has to be  defined as well what can and cannot be updated (may be on wiki page) in terms of priority, some configuration may be more important than other to support initially.   In case we need to stage the dev. in multiple phases.",
