    {
      "id": "74277f2e_28e02b7e",
      "file_path": "models-examples/src/main/resources/policytypes/onap.policies.native.Drools.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 9,
      "line": 18,
      "message": "OK, we can always come back to it and change it if we need to.    \n\nFrom the coordinates we may be able to infer a controller too if there's one installed and running, but if there's not, it will be sitting there with no matching controller \"home\" for it.  That's what I am having more trouble seeing it clear.    What do you guys think to handle this case?",
